| and                     | ∧     | and                  |                                                                     |
| of / imp              | →     | implication          | the conclusion is stated first and the hypotheses are often omitted |
| iff                     | ↔     | if and only if       | sometimes omitted along with the right hand side of the iff         |
| not                     | ¬     | not                  |                                                                     |
| exists / bex          | ∃     | there exists         | bex stands for "bounded exists"                                    |
| all / forall / ball | ∀     | for all              | ball stands for "bounded forall"                                   |
| eq                      | =      | equal                | often omitted in formal theorem names                               |
| ne                      | ≠     | not equal            |                                                                     |
| comp                    | ∘     | function composition |                                                                     |

